---
<footer class="bg-azul-oscuro text-white py-8 px-6 md:px-12 text-center left-0 w-full z-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">
            <a href="#hero" class="text-inherit lato-bold tracking-[0.04em]">Â© 2025 Leandro Barrios Designer</a>
        </p>
